        <mxCell id="5rmcUgci5nsgmCFBUyWv-6" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;In both SM we expected to get frame of data by 640x480. But one of the problem we incountered was the restriction of memory in our FPGA. Our FPGA dont support the amount of this data so I decide to cut pertial of the pixels. In right diagram we can see the solution for this problem&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="640" y="71" width="340" height="130" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
